column4: NSLOCTEXT("[81EAFD2A4369030FB5048FA68270ACA3]", "2598928B4ADB095AC79A1B87FBBBDE1F", "I\'ll give you three pieces of Giant Meat a day.")
NSLOCTEXT("[81EAFD2A4369030FB5048FA68270ACA3]", "E7058CF74B8DF95FA1DC0DACC0094318", "If you want extra, I\'ll sell it to you for five hund bits each.")
NSLOCTEXT("[81EAFD2A4369030FB5048FA68270ACA3]", "917264744842D31F218A9F8DE9713A89", "I\'ll be in charge of this farm for Tanemon. He\'s resting somewhere.")
NSLOCTEXT("[81EAFD2A4369030FB5048FA68270ACA3]", "AFF563AC42A0177E3F24019C0719804C", "Here\'s three pieces of Giant Meat for today.")
NSLOCTEXT("[81EAFD2A4369030FB5048FA68270ACA3]", "96301F904AB0B822671EDB9C2FC6F05D", "I\'ll give you more tomorrow. Or you can buy more now. Five hund bits each?")
